{"tid":1855608,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】私院一罩難求！政府唔派 嘉諾撒醫院建議醫生自備口罩","createTime":"2020-02-01T07:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T07:41:08.000Z","uid":254183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"15fa8e30832f4c498f344a02334070c03ae9ef2e","tid":1855608,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/UuSBYnD_JbO5Q8KfCc7TfWAytAI=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/7ROX5M5QGYT2FQ2XI5KI2D2WWA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FUuSBYnD_JbO5Q8KfCc7TfWAytAI%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F7ROX5M5QGYT2FQ2XI5KI2D2WWA.png&h=38a1306a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎襲港，本港口罩供不應求，嘉諾撒醫院昨日（31日）發電郵給員工指，由於外科口罩及酒精搓手液供應量緊張，要求員工要到「非常有需要」（REALLY NEEDED）時才可訂購，又指口罩只會提供給病房及部門員工，並建議醫生和訪客自行佩戴口罩；酒精搓手液亦只會放在指定地點如病房櫃枱。<br />\n<br />\n嘉諾撒醫院今日（1日）回覆指，該院之口罩數量足夠提供給該院員工和醫生，惟同時會鼓勵醫生或訪客自備口罩。該院暫時沒有收過由政府提供的口罩。<br />\n<br />\n早前約有6,000名私家診所的醫生出現口罩短缺，部份診所更因而未能開門應診，擔心會導致病人被迫轉投公立醫院急症室，加重公營機構負擔。政務司司長張建宗前日會見傳媒時表示，政府已從外國訂購大批口罩，部份已運抵本港，稍後會將部份外科口罩供予醫學會，再由醫學會分發予各診所醫生，惟當中不包括私家醫院。<br />\n<br />\n香港醫學會會長何仲平表示，預計周一會收到政府物流部送來的3萬個應急口罩，料約有600盒，會在下周陸續分發給有需要的私家醫生。他指自己到浸會醫院和法國醫院時，院方都有提供口罩，相信只是少量私家醫院貨源緊張，希望政府可有更多口罩來貨，給私家醫護及員工應急。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戰爭時要士兵自己準備武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ce1f8e2a613d65915c2004892d32f470d1d1df","tid":1855608,"uid":172668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醫護咁都搏命去送死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f711707537cc37aef3cfdf2f1ae237b27f0a334c","tid":1855608,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2HD3SzD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2HD3SzD.jpg&h=e01c6f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#standwithHAEA<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/c/1352779856/117585\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1352779856%2F117585&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IhIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=49917c72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/c/1352779856/117585</a>"},{"pid":"3ec3b158888c594deabde55721d13784bc61e0a6","tid":1855608,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yF0BxP0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyF0BxP0.jpg&h=84e3f7e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Phk9SP0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPhk9SP0.jpg&h=891ee4a9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}